        <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-2 sm:mb-4">On-Time Delivery</h3>
        <p class="text-[13px] sm:text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed">Rigorous project management methodologies to ensure we deliver on schedule, every time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-surface text-center group hover:bg-primary/5 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 mx-auto mb-4 sm:mb-6 bg-primary/5 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
